                <mj-text font-size="18px" color="#000" font-family="helvetica">ğŸƒâ€â™‚ï¸ Running your own Sturdy instance</mj-text>
                <mj-text font-size="14px" color="#555555" font-family="helvetica">
                    We know that for some teams, trying a new SaaS at work involves a lot of red tape. This is why we created an easy way to try Sturdy locally using Docker â€” the setup takes only a few minutes and you can still try most of the features.
                </mj-text>
