                <mj-text font-size="18px" color="#000" font-family="helvetica">ğŸ¢ Introducing organizations</mj-text>
                <mj-text font-size="14px" color="#555555" font-family="helvetica">Sturdy now has organizations. The way it works is simple â€” an organization has members and codebases. Developers who are members of an organization automatically have access to all codebases in the organization.</mj-text>

                <mj-text font-size="14px" color="#555555" font-family="helvetica">As a developer, you can have multiple organizations to create separation â€” for example between personal projects and work.</mj-text>

